<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Grit Gear HQ – Battle-Tested Picks</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: url('images/tt.png') no-repeat center center fixed;
      background-size: cover;
      color: #f2f2f2;
    }

    .overlay {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
      padding: 40px;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 3em;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px #000;
      color: #ffc107;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 25px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .card {
      background: #222;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #ccc;
    }

    .stars {
      color: gold;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background: #ffc107;
      color: #000;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #e0a800;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="overlay">
    <h1>Grit Gear HQ – Battle-Tested Picks</h1>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Tactical Military Backpack</h3>
        <p>Heavy-duty 40L pack. Perfect for bug-outs and tough treks.</p>
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01N6QXXF5" class="btn" target="_blank">Buy Now</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Solar Power Bank</h3>
        <p>Charge phones off-grid. Waterproof and shockproof.</p>
        <div class="stars">★★★★☆</div>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08DKDVS3T" class="btn" target="_blank">Buy Now</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Stun Gun Flashlight Combo</h3>
        <p>Compact defense tool with 90M volts and bright LED.</p>
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B00F44XKL4" class="btn" target="_blank">Buy Now</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Augason Farms 30-Day Food Supply</h3>
        <p>Over 300 meals. Long shelf life and reliable calories.</p>
        <div class="stars">★★★★☆</div>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0096FG0BK" class="btn" target="_blank">Buy Now</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>LifeStraw Personal Water Filter</h3>
        <p>Safe hydration from any water source. Filters up to 1,000 gallons.</p>
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B006QF3TW4" class="btn" target="_blank">Buy Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
